title: Don't Quit Your Gay Job
overview: Rob and Sean are gay and working your gay job....Best friends Rob Easton and Sean Horlor are determined to figure out what it takes to make it "out" there in the big wide world. The premise: Rob and Sean meet someone doing a job. That person teaches them how to do it. And then they compete to see who does it better.Don't Quit Your Gay Job showcases the personal successes and humiliating disappointments of these two friends as they strive to find themselves and new perspectives while learning about gay life on the job.
